{"meta":{"domain":"subjects","kid":"4901","authors":[{"fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre","id":"6"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:26 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:26 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">The copulas <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f60\u0f51\u0f74\u0f42\u0f0b<\/span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f51\u0f0b\u0f62\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span>, etc. are not used in future constructions. Instead, the future forms of the full verbs <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f46\u0f42\u0f66\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cto become,\u201d <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0fb1\u0f7a\u0f51\u0f0b<\/span> \u201cto do,\u201d <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b <\/span>\u201cto come,\u201d<a name=\"n1\" href=\"#fn1\">[1]<\/a> and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f56\u0f66\u0fa1\u0f51\u0f0b <\/span>\u201cto stay\u201d are used. A distinction may be made between essential and existential statements.<\/p><hr size=\"1\" \/><p><a name=\"fn1\" href=\"#n1\">[1]<\/a> Note that <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">\u0f61\u0f7c\u0f44\u0f0b<\/span> may also mean \u201cto be appropriate.\u201d<\/p>","title":""}]}